{"tid":1479960,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"陳雲：勇武社運要set rules?屌你老母","createTime":"2019-08-17T06:05:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-17T22:06:24.000Z","uid":5195,"like":79,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4602c2ce8c7a8f1d6a5c3899d7c19f8cc3033096","tid":1479960,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:05:53.000Z","msg":"陳雲：戰場問答。<br />\n某論壇：各位，我們是一群倫理學家、醫生、i-bankers、IT從業員...現在要set rules關於勇武社運。<br />\n陳雲：屌你老母呀。戰役打完，勝利在即，你才set rules？要製造曼德拉效應，令大家以為你set 了rules之後才打贏的嗎？陳雲不是一開始就set了rules嗎：無名無姓，不言不語，隨機變陣，流水社運。<br />\n我們就快打贏啦。馬拉松到了最後一段路，泛民才作狀加入跑步，最後衝出來靠害，令我們失足絆倒。"},{"pid":"590e061cb607f47cf0dda3ae556357f378993ef1","tid":1479960,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:07:28.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2c391f5438704f10ad675405cef17fb15b037400","tid":1479960,"uid":149630,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:07:39.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"663ff0eafdfd0c7f3cc62062449219138edc8175","tid":1479960,"uid":10778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:07:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32cb1387dd7508f47960d70bec5966e12140b5be","tid":1479960,"uid":12773,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:08:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a182392b1e4b3586805f4dfc632cc370c296b3b8","tid":1479960,"uid":49144,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T06:08:46.000Z","msg":"國師又中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/norm